casebody.head_matter:
Robert BIROS, petitioner,
v.
Kathleen KANE, Attorney General of Pennsylvania, et al.
No. 15-910.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 2, 2016.
Motion of respondents for leave to file a brief in opposition under seal granted. Motion of petitioner for leave to file a reply brief under seal granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Common Pleas of Pennsylvania, Allegheny County denied.
